# 6. SYN Scan

## Objective

Perform a stealth TCP scan.

## Command

```bash
sudo nmap -sS <TARGET-IP>
```

## Output File

```bash
sudo nmap -sS <TARGET-IP> -oN raw-output/syn-scan.txt
```

## Explanation

- `-sS` performs a SYN scan.
- Faster than TCP Connect.
- More stealthy.
- Requires root privileges.

